{"tid":2375452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔣麗芸：曾免息借錢給街坊度難關　斥政府抗疫不力","createTime":"2021-01-22T05:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T06:07:13.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a20145127164eadb3002dc3275a4af3d06a86843","tid":2375452,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:05:13.000Z","msg":"民建聯蔣麗芸批評政府抗疫不力，政策議而不決，決而不行，不少市民受到經濟下滑影響，她近日亦要免息借錢給街坊度過難關。她指，特首林鄭月娥多番表示要以清零為目標，如果疫情在社區進一步擴散，政府就應該實施全民強制檢測、疫苗接種和健康碼三管齊下，否則香港只會在疫情下拖拖拉拉，很多企業將要倒閉。 立法會今日將結束致謝議案辯論，在多名建制派議員表態支持下，預料議案將獲得通過。"},{"pid":"0d8d6b70edca67df404664e1b9865bab7b9e49df","tid":2375452,"uid":241146,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:06:27.000Z","msg":"我都有難關，多謝蔣議員"},{"pid":"282f438be71a3bdbc61c9567641ab93c5983a864","tid":2375452,"uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:07:24.000Z","msg":"借俾我，我100年後還 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a979e6824d3fd874576f482e21f590ca8f2c02bb","tid":2375452,"uid":381575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:08:00.000Z","msg":"叫政府派錢未"},{"pid":"11912d6db5c0387b483df7cd313324c94239e007","tid":2375452,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cache.hkgolden.media/compress/https://na.cx/i/uCP2fGu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcache.hkgolden.media%2Fcompress%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCP2fGu.gif&h=1ca3b276&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d0a1a9fde92ac870519815f036a876cf5f920dd","tid":2375452,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:10:26.000Z","msg":"借比我啦"},{"pid":"6226d02e749e3c62e1a4bb18b647ae76e422dcc3","tid":2375452,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:11:25.000Z","msg":"借比我啦元秋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ador